    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fiora 一款 Roguelike 游戏，在其中你会看到随机生成的地图，你需要与暗影战斗，并一路收集木材来为菲奥娜的火焰提供燃料，没有木材你将无法使用魔法。<br>感受这种类型中不寻常的动态游戏，使用躲避，思考路线，推开阻碍你的障碍:)<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3293800/extras/2313a72e76b93631d39e22de1765ab8e.poster.avif?t=1769597528\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3293800/extras/2313a72e76b93631d39e22de1765ab8e.webm?t=1769597528\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3293800/extras/2313a72e76b93631d39e22de1765ab8e.mp4?t=1769597528\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>收集水晶油来提高你的武器的性能。目前，游戏有三种类型的武器，四种类别，并且可以将它们升级到+20，最重要的是不要忘记，升级后，武器可能会损坏并从你的库存中消失<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3293800/extras/60229028f59f3a37f4e9ae86313e52cb.poster.avif?t=1769597528\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3293800/extras/60229028f59f3a37f4e9ae86313e52cb.webm?t=1769597528\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3293800/extras/60229028f59f3a37f4e9ae86313e52cb.mp4?t=1769597528\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>与不时出现或在某些事件期间出现的头目和特殊敌人战斗<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3293800/extras/9f52885193ef2f7c2239dbb11b891339.poster.avif?t=1769597528\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3293800/extras/9f52885193ef2f7c2239dbb11b891339.webm?t=1769597528\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3293800/extras/9f52885193ef2f7c2239dbb11b891339.mp4?t=1769597528\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
